WF-007 | Reset all active filters | actor: <role> | branch: Active_Filters_Summary.item_count > 0 | terminal: Reset all | on_success: clears all filters and updates results
WF-008 | Initiate booking from a hotel card | actor: <role> | branch: none | terminal: Book Now | on_success: initiates booking flow for selected hotel
